d 379 in 2001.<ref>[http://www12.statcan.ca/english/census06/data/popdwell/Table.cfm?T=302&SR=626&S=1&O=A&RPP=25&PR=59&CMA=0 Statistics Canada, 2006 Census]</ref> The village lies off the coast of [[Hardwicke Island]].\n\n==See also==\n*[[Sayward Valley]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.sayward.ca/ Village of Sayward]\n\n{{VancouverIslandCommunities}}\n{{Subdivisions of British Columbia|village=yes}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in British Columbia]]\n[[Category:Northern Vancouver Island]]\n[[Category:Populated places in the Strathcona Regional District]]\n", "name_user": "Infogapp1", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added external resource for William Parsons Sayward since there's no wiki page for him", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sayward"}
